亦有认为，反应历程首先为锂化合物对酯羰基的加成，然后发生消除，生成二溴烯醇锂盐，再锂化，并发生α-消除得到烯基[[卡宾|卡宾]]、发生烷基迁移，从而最后醇解，得酯。[http://books.google.com/books?id=ahRrPTfeqPEC&pg=PA44&lpg=PA44&dq=Kowalski+ester&source=bl&ots=ccHFw0hDnE&sig=ZjV9Betkt_0dcrEEV4neiphJTxw&hl=en&ei=hQHjSoC9AtTykAXL2by2AQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7&ved=0CB4Q6AEwBjgK#v=onepage&q=Kowalski%20ester&f=false 图]

